            <title>[DATAREST-411] BaseUrl mapping not workig</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAREST-411</link>
                <project id="10901" key="DATAREST">Spring Data REST</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Not sure if the issue is with Data-Rest or Spring Boot but extending RepositoryRestConfiguration and setting a BaseUri (to say /rest) using 1.1.9.RELEASE move the list repository controller from / to /rest allowing / to get to the index.html page in src/main/resource/public/ amending to version&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.springframework.boot&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;spring-boot-starter-parent&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;version&amp;gt;1.2.0.M2&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Make the list repository controller work on BOTH / and /rest&lt;/p&gt;</description>
